Jagodnik  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Milejewo, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  west of Milejewo,  north-east of Elbląg, and  north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
